reviewText: I GOT THIS FOR A GIFT AND IT IS IN GOOD CONDITION.  I HAVEN'T PLAYED IT AS IT IS A GIFT BUT I AM FAMILIAR WITH THE SERIES AND THIS STORY IS PARTICULARLY EXCITING.  MY GRANDKIDS LOVE, IT.

The Final Conflict brings the Story Keepers to a close in a very loving and joyful way.
I have 4 adopted grandchildren, and it's wonderful for them to see how the Lord provides
loving homes for those who "lose" their parents--and how he restores some of them to
their birth parents.  My grandchildren loves these stories.
Came on time and DVD is in good playable condition. Cover was there with cover insert in fairly good condition less some nail marks presumably from the last owners dog. Well worth the money!!
I am very pleased with this purchase.  I have wanted to collect all the DVDs in this series so this was a great addition.  It came quickly and without any problem at all.
